body.bgspot

    main.mdl-layout__content.page-content
      div(data-hook="welcome-info")

      div.content-grid.mdl-grid.mdl-cell--middle
        div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--8-col.mdl-cell--2-offset.mdl-shadow--2dp.spot-cell.spot-trans.spot-color4
          span.cardTitleText.fa.fa-flask
          span.cardTitleText  SPOT: interactive, fast facet browser
          ul
            li
              p.cardText SPOT is an interactive, fast, multi-dimensional data visualization tool developed for iDARK Project.
            li
              p.cardText Purposes of the project are: to allow the storage, publication, visualization and comparison of model-solutions for Dark Matter in the full parameter space "on-line". The developed code will be reusable to visualize solution spaces for other purpose. This prototype contains the data of two recent papers on Dark Matter shown in blue and green in the plots. A few parameters and observables are free to choose, finally more than 100 observables and parameters can be included for each model point. The final tool can store solution points for multiple publications.

        div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col.spot-cell.spot-trans.spot-color4
          span.cardTitleText.fa.fa-bolt
          span.cardTitleText   Highlights
          ul
            li
              .cardText Specifically designed for scientific data visualization
            li
              .cardText Fully animated and interactive charts
            li
              .cardText Exploration sessions can be saved
            li
              .cardText Database connection (Postgresql)

        div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col.spot-cell.spot-trans.spot-color4
          span.cardTitleText.fa.fa-font-awesome
          span.cardTitleText   Modern tools
          ul
            li
              .cardText Viewer is fully standalone (no server required)
            li
              .cardText Responsive interface: material design lite
            li
              .cardText Fast filtering (~1M data points in ~30ms)
            li
              .cardText Cross platform (desktop, mobile and tablet)

        div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col.mdl-shadow--2dp.spot-cell.spot-trans.spot-color4
          span.cardTitleText.fa.fa-github
          span.cardTitleText   Open Source
          ul
            li
              .cardText Permissive Open source Licence (Apache 2.0)
            li
              .cardText Continuous Integration
            li
              .cardText Documented (jsdoc) and tested (jasmine)
            li
              .cardText Generic tool to be useful in any scientific project

      div.mdl-layout-spacer


